            "text": "A lot of confusion comes about from well-intentioned mothers telling their children they can become anything they want to be as long as their put their mind to it. We see the effects all around us, and it unfortunately has bled into the automotive world. A prime case is this 1991 Camaro which wears a 2011 COPO Camaro body kit. Just looking at this thing should fill you with confusion.",
